Description: The Petrol engine is 4395 cc . It is available with Automatic transmission. Depending upon the variant and fuel type the M5 has a mileage of 9.12 kmpl . The M5 is a 5 seater 8 cylinder car and has length of 4983mm, width of 2126mm and a wheelbase of 2982mm.

The GLE Coupe isn't the quickest in the class, but it handles very well and is exceptionally easy to drive in every situation. It also boasts a modern and luxurious interior. Our main complaint centers on the stiff ride and compromised cargo capacity.
